d\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"1em\" height=\"1em\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 256 256\"><path d=\"M224,128a8,8,0,0,1-8,8H40a8,8,0,0,1,0-16H216A8,8,0,0,1,224,128ZM40,72H216a8,8,0,0,0,0-16H40a8,8,0,0,0,0,16ZM216,184H40a8,8,0,0,0,0,16H216a8,8,0,0,0,0-16Z\"></path></svg></button></div></header><div class=\"w-full px-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto pt-32 pb-20\"><div class=\"mb-10\"><h1 class=\"text-4xl font-bold mb-4\">Blog</h1><p class=\"text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400\">Thoughts, stories, and ideas about web development, design, and technology.</p></div><div class=\"w-full\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-10\" role=\"tablist\" aria-label=\"Blog categories\"><button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"blog-posts\" id=\"tab-all\" class=\"rounded-full px-4 py-1 text-sm bg-teal-500 text-white\">All</button><button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"blog-posts\" id=\"tab-open-source\" class=\"rounded-full px-4 py-1 text-sm bg-neutral-200 dark:bg-neutral-800 text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 hover:bg-teal-500 hover:text-white transition-colors\">Open Source</button><button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"blog-posts\" id=\"tab-product-engineering\" class=\"rounded-full px-4 py-1 text-sm bg-neutral-200 dark:bg-neutral-800 text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 hover:bg-teal-500 hover:text-white transition-colors\">Product Engineering</button><button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"blog-posts\" id=\"tab-philosophy\" class=\"rounded-full px-4 py-1 text-sm bg-neutral-200 dark:bg-neutral-800 text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 hover:bg-teal-500 hover:text-white transition-colors\">Philosophy</button></div><div id=\"blog-posts\" role=\"tabpanel\" class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8\"><a class=\"group flex flex-col rounded-lg overflow-hidden border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 hover:border-teal-500 dark:hover:border-teal-500 transition-all hover:shadow-md\" href=\"/blog/why-i-bet-on-open-source-agents\"><div class=\"relative h-48 w-full overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative size-full\"><img alt=\"Cover image for Why I Bet on Open Source AI Agents\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover size-full transition-transform group-hover:scale-105\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, (max-width: 1024px) 50vw, 384px\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fopensource.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fopensource.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fopensource.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fopensource.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fopensource.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fopensource.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fopensource.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fopensource.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fopensource.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fopensource.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-neutral-900/70 to-transparent\"></div></div><div class=\"absolute top-4 left-4 bg-neutral-900/70 text-white text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full\">Philosophy</div></div><div class=\"p-5 grow flex flex-col\"><div class=\"flex items-center text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400 mb-2\"><span>November 10, 2025</span><span class=\"mx-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\">•</span><span>5 min read</span></div><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-2 group-hover:text-teal-500 transition-colors\">Why I Bet on Open Source AI Agents</h2><p class=\"text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 text-sm mb-4 line-clamp-2\">Closed ecosystem agents are a dead end. The real innovation is happening where tools can talk to each other without asking for permission. Here is why I am betting my career on Open Source AI.</p><div class=\"mt-auto flex items-center text-teal-500 text-sm font-medium\">Read article<svg class=\"ml-1 size-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><title>Arrow right</title><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3\"></path></svg></div></div></a><a class=\"group flex flex-col rounded-lg overflow-hidden border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 hover:border-teal-500 dark:hover:border-teal-500 transition-all hover:shadow-md\" href=\"/blog/connecting-terminals-to-web-mconnect\"><div class=\"relative h-48 w-full overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative size-full\"><img alt=\"Cover image for Connecting Terminals to the Web: The mconnect Story\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover size-full transition-transform group-hover:scale-105\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, (max-width: 1024px) 50vw, 384px\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fmconnect.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fmconnect.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fmconnect.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fmconnect.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fmconnect.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fmconnect.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fmconnect.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fmconnect.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fmconnect.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fmconnect.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-neutral-900/70 to-transparent\"></div></div><div class=\"absolute top-4 left-4 bg-neutral-900/70 text-white text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full\">Open Source</div></div><div class=\"p-5 grow flex flex-col\"><div class=\"flex items-center text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400 mb-2\"><span>October 15, 2025</span><span class=\"mx-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\">•</span><span>6 min read</span></div><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-2 group-hover:text-teal-500 transition-colors\">Connecting Terminals to the Web: The mconnect Story</h2><p class=\"text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 text-sm mb-4 line-clamp-2\">Coding agents like Claude and Cursor live in the terminal, but I wanted to control them from my phone. Here is how I built mconnect to solve the &#x27;coffee shop problem&#x27;.</p><div class=\"mt-auto flex items-center text-teal-500 text-sm font-medium\">Read article<svg class=\"ml-1 size-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><title>Arrow right</title><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3\"></path></svg></div></div></a><a class=\"group flex flex-col rounded-lg overflow-hidden border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 hover:border-teal-500 dark:hover:border-teal-500 transition-all hover:shadow-md\" href=\"/blog/building-lesearch-from-papers-to-action\"><div class=\"relative h-48 w-full overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative size-full\"><img alt=\"Cover image for Building LeSearch: From Papers to Action\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover size-full transition-transform group-hover:scale-105\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, (max-width: 1024px) 50vw, 384px\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Flesearch.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Flesearch.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Flesearch.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Flesearch.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Flesearch.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Flesearch.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Flesearch.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Flesearch.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Flesearch.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Flesearch.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-neutral-900/70 to-transparent\"></div></div><div class=\"absolute top-4 left-4 bg-neutral-900/70 text-white text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full\">Product Engineering</div></div><div class=\"p-5 grow flex flex-col\"><div class=\"flex items-center text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400 mb-2\"><span>September 1, 2025</span><span class=\"mx-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\">•</span><span>8 min read</span></div><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-2 group-hover:text-teal-500 transition-colors\">Building LeSearch: From Papers to Action</h2><p class=\"text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 text-sm mb-4 line-clamp-2\">Research is broken. We read 100 papers to use 1. I built LeSearch AI to turn static PDFs into active knowledge graphs and actionable insights.</p><div class=\"mt-auto flex items-center text-teal-500 text-sm font-medium\">Read article<svg class=\"ml-1 size-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><title>Arrow right</title><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3\"></path></svg></div></div></a></div></div></div></main><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer id=\"contact\" class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0 relative mt-32 pb-6 overflow-hidden bg-neutral-950\"><div class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0 absolute inset-0 -z-10 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0 absolute inset-0 bg-neutral-950\"></div><div class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0 stars-small absolute inset-0\"></div><div class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0 stars-medium absolute inset-0\"></div><div class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0 absolute left-1/2 top-2/3 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[500px] h-[300px] rounded-full bg-teal-500/5 blur-[100px]\"></div><div class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0 absolute left-1/2 top-2/3 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[300px] h-[150px] rounded-full bg-teal-400/10 blur-[60px]\"></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0 w-full px-4 md:max-w-4xl lg:px-0 m-auto pt-16\"><div class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 mb-16\"><div class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0\"><h3 class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0 text-2xl font-bold mb-4\">Arya Teja .</h3><p class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0 text-gray-400 mb-6 font-light leading-relaxed\">Building<!-- --> <span class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0 text-teal-400 font-medium\">mconnect</span>. An open source initiative from<!-- --> <span class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0 text-teal-400 font-medium\">LeSearch AI</span> <!-- -->that connects terminals to the web.<br class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0\"/><span class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0 text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2 block\">Dev since Dec 2025.</span></p></div><div class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0 text-lg font-semibold mb-6\">Quick Links</h4><nav class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0 flex flex-col space-y-3\"><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-400 transition-colors\" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-400 transition-colors\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-400 transition-colors\" href=\"/projects\">Projects</a><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-400 transition-colors\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-400 transition-colors\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></nav></div><div class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0 space-y-8\"><div class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a6510013d76296b0 text-lg font-semibold mb-6\">Get in Touch</h4><div class=\"jsx-a6510013d762